  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Oral and intravenous glutathione have been used widely to whiten the skin. The investigators
      tested this hypothesis by giving oral glutathione for 4 weeks to medical students.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>February 2009</start_date>
